v_{1}, v_{2}, .., v_{k}, .., v_{n}
\{v_{1}, v_{2}, .., v_{k}\}
span(S) = c_{1}v_{1}+c_{2}v_{2}+ .. +c_{k}v_{k}
c_{1}, c_{2},.., c_{k} \in F
{\bf0} \in span(S)
c_{1},..,c_{k} = 0
{\bf x}, {\bf y}\in span(S)
{\bf x} = c_{1}v_{1}+c_{2}v_{2}+..+c_{k}v_{k}
{\bf y} = d_{1}v_{1}+d_{2}v_{2}+..+d_{k}v_{k}
c_{1},..,c_{k}, d_{1},..d_{k} \in F
\lambda \in F
{\bf x} + \lambda {\bf y} = c_{1}v_{1}+c_{2}v_{2}+..+c_{k}v_{k} + \lambda (d_{1}v_{1}+d_{2}v_{2}+..+d_{k}v_{k})
=(c_{1}+\lambda d_{1})v_{1}+(c_{2}+\lambda d_{2})v_{2}+..+(c_{k}+\lambda d_{k})v_{k}
(c_{k}+\lambda d_{k}) \in F
{\bf x} + \lambda {\bf y} \in span(S)
